content:
Self-Service reports help you analyze the effectiveness of your Self-Service portal. Find out how many cases are being viewed, how many customers are logging in, or what customers think of the solutions youâ€™re offering.

Available in: Salesforce Classic
Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

The Self-Service Usage Report gives information on case views, comments added, and searches performed.
The Self-Service User Report provides information about customers logging into your portal, including account and last login date.
You can also include Self-Service fields in custom contact reports.

The Helpful Solutions report displays statistics from Self-Service portals showing helpful solutions. Customers indicate whether solutions are helpful on each solution page.
title: Self-Service Reporting in Salesforce
